data.description: Welcome to your exquisite residence on Alhi! As you approach this expansive ranch-style home, you'll be captivated by the generous lot, meticulously landscaped yard, and the allure of a freshly laid driveway. Upon entering, the open floor plan welcomes you with an abundance of natural light, creating a warm and cheerful atmosphere throughout the year.  Discover the joy of cozy evenings immersed in a captivating book by the fireplace, or unleash your culinary prowess in the spacious chef's kitchen that seamlessly connects to the dining room – perfect for intimate dinners or lively gatherings. The main floor boasts three delightful bedrooms, including a master suite with an attached bath for your utmost comfort.  Venture downstairs to find two bonus bedrooms, an additional living area or rec room, and an extra bath, providing an ideal space for in-laws or expanding your recreational activities. Outside, a splendid large patio beckons for evenings around the firepit or hosting lively summer barbecues.  This home is a harmonious blend of elegance and functionality, offering a total of 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, providing ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. There are also 2 Garages one attached and one detached! All this on a huge nearly half acre lot. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home sweet home!
